                   CharSequence exchange,
                   CharSequence walletAddress,
                   RiskLevel riskLevel,
                   CharSequence sessionId,
                   CharSequence ipAddress)
        All-args constructor.
        Parameters:
        tradeId - Unique trade identifier
        userId - User identifier
        customerId - Customer account identifier
        symbol - Trading pair symbol e.g., BTC/USDT
        baseAsset - Base asset e.g., BTC
        quoteAsset - Quote asset e.g., USDT
        side - Trade side
        orderType - Order type
        quantity - Trade quantity in base asset
        price - Trade price in quote asset
        notional - Notional value (quantity * price)
        timestamp - Event timestamp in milliseconds
        exchange - Exchange identifier
        walletAddress - Associated wallet address
        riskLevel - Initial risk assessment
        sessionId - Trading session identifier
        ipAddress - User IP address
